story.text: I wander through many news streams on The 'Net in my daily life. In this wiki I collect insights that capture my attention or ask to be remembered. See [[Commonplace Book]].

Among other things, I am a programmer by recreation. My career has turned towards learning from incidents in complex software systems. These interests have an outsized influence over the events that capture my attention.

item.text: I wander through many news streams on The 'Net in my daily life. This wiki is my commonplace book for collecting the insights that capture my attention or look like something I might want to remember.
